<paragraph id="9D4D36A8FFF2257EFF02573DFE84C36F" blockId="3.[149,380,1850,1873]" box="[149,380,1850,1873]" pageId="3" pageNumber="498">Biology.—Unknown.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="D5E86523FFF2257EFF02576DFD9FC3A0" pageId="3" pageNumber="498" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="9D4D36A8FFF2257EFF02576DFD9FC3A0" blockId="3.[149,742,1898,1950]" pageId="3" pageNumber="498">Etymology —Named in honor of the inhabitants of Pomerode, the type-locality of the species.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
